longBusinessSummary: Alpha Networks Inc. engages in the research and development, design, production, and sale of broadband products, computer network systems, wireless local area networks, and related accessories in Taiwan, Singapore, China, the United States, and internationally. The company's LAN/MAN products include data center, enterprise campus, small business, carrier access, and industrial ethernet network products; and wireless broadband products, such as mobile broadband, fixed broadband access, and wireless networking products. It also provides digital multimedia products, which include IP cameras; and mobile enterprise solutions, such as radar sensors, smart doorbells, T-box, AVM, and ADAS solutions. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Hsinchu City, Taiwan. Alpha Networks Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Qisda Corporation.
